Kia ora! Ka whakaratohia e ahau he tohutao ki te hanga i tetahi taputapu pupuhi kaainga. Me whakamahi i ēnei āpurenga hei āwhina i a koe:

1. Whakararuraru i te whenua: Whakarite he whakararuraru pai i te whenua, kia whakapapaku i ngā rākau, ngā rāwekeweke, me ngā pūrerehua. Whakararuraru i ngā pūweto, ka whakatika i ngā ngārara i te taputapu pupuhi kaainga.

2. Whakatū i te taputapu pupuhi kaainga: Whakatū i te taputapu pupuhi kaainga ki te wāhi e hiahia ana koe ki te pupuhi i te haere. Kia whakamahi i te kaha o te hau, whakatū i te taputapu ki te taha o te whare, ki te wharangi, ki te taha o te wharepaku, rānei.

3. Whakamahi i te kaainga: Whakamahi i te kaainga hei whakararuraru i te huarahi o ngā ngārara. Kia whakatika i te kaainga i te taha o te taputapu pupuhi kaainga, whakamahi i te rama, te pūrerehua rānei ki te whakatika i ngā ngārara.

4. Whakararuraru i ngā whare: Whakararuraru i ngā whare ki te whakararuraru i ngā ngārara. Whakamahi i te kaha o te hau ki te whakararuraru i ngā rūma, ngā tāpapa, ngā wharepaku, me ngā wāhi noho.

5. Whakararuraru i ngā wāhi e noho ana ngā ngārara: T
